BUG-18008E90	bug_18008e90	Workflow CLI frontdoor eagerly imports a stale workflow command table and bricks the whole namespace	FIXED	P1	P1	surfaces/cli/main.py imports the entire workflow command table at module import time, including stale command symbols. That means one missing export can take down the whole praxis workflow namespace b	manual	\N	\N	\N		\N	2026-04-16 16:15:17.557509-07	2026-04-17 03:09:44.266028-07	2026-04-16 16:15:17.557509-07	2026-04-17 03:09:44.266028-07	ARCHITECTURE	surfaces/cli/main.py imports the entire workflow command table at module import time, including stale command symbols. That means one missing export can take down the whole praxis workflow namespace before dispatch starts, instead of failing only the affected subcommand. Observed during bug discovery: importing praxis workflow bugs stats and other workflow entrypoints raises ImportError from surfaces.cli.main. Relevant files: surfaces/cli/main.py, surfaces/cli/commands/workflow.py.	codex	\N		[-0.065358,-0.070785,-0.032154,0.017829,0.070367,-0.090281,-0.037768,-0.01009,-0.016308,-0.04267,0.003658,-0.023296,0.030043,0.008687,0.054251,0.034516,-0.058259,-0.028951,-0.005044,0.017401,-0.019648,0.107891,0.003588,-0.015472,-0.069368,-0.014136,-0.053917,0.008247,0.022712,-0.020707,-0.066817,0.162761,0.040676,-0.016959,0.121921,0.143518,-0.027212,-0.007674,0.023314,-0.026149,0.088029,0.033384,-0.023158,-0.020994,-0.067854,-0.069262,0.049663,-0.079926,-0.04599,0.005586,-0.021152,-0.01888,0.030525,-0.042362,0.049878,0.059682,0.010395,0.018535,0.03252,-0.017305,-0.079344,0.032977,-0.000188,-0.043072,-0.026306,-0.02192,-0.043456,-0.030394,0.046108,0.023808,-0.039519,0.038269,-0.114985,-0.012012,0.010427,-0.014069,0.072787,-0.027403,-0.070803,-0.141111,-0.025975,0.022753,-0.06914,0.039425,0.055547,0.04278,0.005052,-0.022908,0.048749,-0.013976,-0.039867,-0.121042,-0.002143,0.103582,-0.05236,0.048362,0.013989,0.039194,-0.09384,0.004082,-0.052382,-0.05653,0.07746,0.054163,0.011305,0.037794,0.044867,