BUG-988212E7	bug_988212e7	Legacy /ui redirect shim remains in the FastAPI front door	FIXED	P2	P2	The FastAPI app still exposes /ui, /ui/, and /ui/{path:path} only as redirect shims to /app via _legacy_ui_redirect in Code&DBs/Workflow/surfaces/api/rest.py:3215-3233. The canonical launcher surface 	manual	\N	\N	\N		\N	2026-04-16 21:07:27.533056-07	2026-04-16 22:00:58.843749-07	2026-04-16 21:07:27.533056-07	2026-04-16 22:00:58.843749-07	WIRING	The FastAPI app still exposes /ui, /ui/, and /ui/{path:path} only as redirect shims to /app via _legacy_ui_redirect in Code&DBs/Workflow/surfaces/api/rest.py:3215-3233. The canonical launcher surface is /app, and the test suite only verifies that /ui redirects there (Code&DBs/Workflow/tests/unit/test_api_rest_startup.py:359-365). This is compatibility-only behavior with no owning logic, so it should be removed once no clients depend on the legacy path. Cleanup value: reduce duplicated front-door surface area and eliminate a stale redirect branch that can drift from the real launcher app.	codex	\N		[-0.001509,0.042061,0.041203,0.001744,0.0051,-0.08953,-0.1045,-0.012666,-0.062784,-0.04675,0.025416,0.022789,0.03357,0.018618,0.089494,-0.006442,0.015704,0.040936,0.053195,0.065616,-0.00144,-0.023904,-0.006844,0.003614,-0.077592,-0.111613,-0.015576,-0.011159,-0.003736,-0.018042,0.003848,0.086088,-0.084053,-0.058032,0.031811,0.032949,0.023577,-0.086226,0.019585,0.008143,0.073497,0.029745,-0.01073,-0.011482,0.059031,-0.034159,0.014329,-0.040117,-0.022393,0.048954,0.043456,0.020942,-0.015537,-2.6e-05,0.001291,0.003757,-0.02287,0.056256,0.034858,0.059144,0.040443,-0.041488,0.081163,-0.074146,0.003377,-0.032252,-0.064289,-0.050035,0.022524,0.00219,0.029825,-0.011364,-0.041932,-0.086427,0.062265,-0.045535,-0.017733,0.072271,-0.048635,-0.128371,0.051632,-0.039366,-0.045671,0.072212,0.078769,0.064182,-0.022552,-0.059896,0.036908,0.027321,0.041126,-0.111142,0.001371,-0.012761,0.060054,-0.058019,-0.060356,0.009884,-0.056237,0.040363,0.024445,-0.0