BUG-1A4291CE	bug_1a4291ce	RouteOutcomeStore hides metrics-view failures by returning empty history and provider lists	FIXED	P2	P2	RouteOutcomeStore._metrics_view(), _db_recent_outcomes(), and _db_provider_slugs() all swallow import/query exceptions and return None or empty tuples. That means a broken workflow_metrics view or que	code_inspection	\N	\N	\N		\N	2026-04-16 16:28:17.477566-07	2026-04-17 01:05:20.198617-07	2026-04-16 16:28:17.477566-07	2026-04-17 01:05:20.198617-07	VERIFY	RouteOutcomeStore._metrics_view(), _db_recent_outcomes(), and _db_provider_slugs() all swallow import/query exceptions and return None or empty tuples. That means a broken workflow_metrics view or query path is indistinguishable from a genuinely empty history, so route health and provider discovery can look healthy while the durable metrics authority is offline or malformed. Evidence: Code&DBs/Workflow/runtime/route_outcomes.py lines 294-306, 316-327, and 368-375.	codex	\N		[0.004524,-0.047894,-0.017908,0.062552,0.005303,-0.027301,-0.063649,0.001347,-0.0024,-0.05601,-0.029747,0.005864,-0.034948,7.8e-05,-0.091033,0.01335,0.016085,-0.080454,0.005211,-0.015311,-0.058623,0.092064,0.015657,0.091767,-0.005194,-0.034576,-0.059715,-0.047305,-0.00879,0.013776,0.021401,0.033268,-0.067955,0.02379,0.07409,0.024897,0.035372,0.003646,-0.044158,-0.061695,0.051197,0.063467,0.007975,0.059705,-0.022455,-0.077904,-0.038438,-0.046622,-0.025399,-0.001861,-0.083751,0.02103,0.010849,0.017043,0.083263,0.077761,-0.062026,0.035704,-0.085476,-0.003583,0.014205,-0.050243,-0.008396,-0.016423,-0.006908,0.015904,0.031605,-0.050086,0.022927,0.015304,-0.051056,-0.020222,-0.094551,0.064484,0.067241,0.051847,0.012175,-0.06033,-0.008439,-0.088267,0.013685,0.025479,-0.003592,0.113409,0.090671,-0.052855,0.030312,-0.08017,0.079623,-0.039179,-0.004219,-0.026273,-0.026644,-0.029698,0.023682,-0.022114,-0.040141,-0.018997,-0.019703,0.026331,-0.058298,-0.00491,0.04491,0.060943,0.023704,0.046519,0.036172,0.002374,0.043845,0.079546,0