BUG-16C42B8B	bug_16c42b8b	Operator roadmap surfaces reject omitted optional payload fields	FIXED	P2	P2	The canonical operator roadmap frontdoor mishandles omitted optional payload fields. `praxis_operator_write` forwards omitted sequence fields like `depends_on` and `registry_paths` as None into tuple-	code_inspection	\N	\N	\N		\N	2026-04-17 02:38:28.231949-07	2026-04-17 02:39:24.268965-07	2026-04-17 02:38:28.231949-07	2026-04-17 02:39:24.268965-07	WIRING	The canonical operator roadmap frontdoor mishandles omitted optional payload fields. `praxis_operator_write` forwards omitted sequence fields like `depends_on` and `registry_paths` as None into tuple-backed command contracts, while the tool-call payload contract treats blank optional text as invalid and causes `praxis_operator_roadmap_view --input-json '{}'` to fail with a non-empty `decision_ref` error. Impact: valid default roadmap preview/read calls fail at the operator surface instead of resolving through the catalog-backed authority.	codex	\N		[-0.018279,0.00057,-0.014945,-0.010398,-0.049277,-0.054667,-0.051825,0.035853,-0.074331,0.023795,0.013013,-0.0527,0.000511,0.001564,0.087697,0.063304,0.000764,-0.057027,0.028083,0.01098,-0.005465,0.070947,-0.05502,-0.034457,-0.050724,-0.033004,-0.011832,0.035914,0.034041,-0.032006,-0.033244,0.046358,0.012185,-0.052149,0.108157,0.134457,0.024722,-0.076309,-0.057705,-0.031912,0.023795,0.024001,-0.071871,0.047319,0.003458,-0.12324,0.074522,-0.095215,-0.051102,-0.002386,-0.067287,0.032591,-0.017236,-0.012267,-0.037117,0.016807,-0.108348,0.024695,0.005811,-0.028361,-0.092978,-0.012115,-0.063907,-0.031394,0.013395,-0.023744,-0.008378,-0.082792,0.012958,0.067495,-0.014702,-0.002643,-0.066551,0.001423,0.04344,0.08821,0.009872,0.004383,-0.008485,-0.151316,-0.014333,0.026497,-0.037254,0.045915,0.012063,-0.026975,-0.039132,-0.035588,0.112951,0.080146,0.032979,-0.148369,0.024789,0.045201,-0.03123,0.018525,-0.015107,-0.051606,-0.081799,0.024286,-0.057194,-0.060391,0.025409,0.048308,0