BUG-11C8C161	bug_11c8c161	Workflow query route families are dead adapters that still trampoline into legacy workflow_query.py	FIXED	P2	P2	The modular query handler files under surfaces/api/handlers/_query_*.py do not own behavior; they are thin trampolines that immediately call legacy workflow_query.py handlers. This creates split autho	manual	\N	\N	\N		\N	2026-04-16 16:15:25.282765-07	2026-04-17 02:54:06.529671-07	2026-04-16 16:15:25.282765-07	2026-04-17 02:54:06.529671-07	WIRING	The modular query handler files under surfaces/api/handlers/_query_*.py do not own behavior; they are thin trampolines that immediately call legacy workflow_query.py handlers. This creates split authority with a fake modular boundary: fixes can land in the new family without changing runtime behavior, or vice versa, and the code will keep drifting because the new files are not authoritative. Relevant files include _query_catalog.py, _query_objects.py, _query_files.py, _query_dashboard.py, and _query_workflows.py, all forwarding to workflow_query.py.	codex	\N		[-0.061187,-0.053107,0.008816,0.035326,-0.008374,-0.141554,-0.036842,-0.002704,-0.033363,-0.056666,-0.012739,0.067,-0.012997,0.006065,0.031289,0.046532,-0.029399,-0.032989,-0.043896,0.006042,0.021083,0.058381,-0.003045,0.033133,-0.098854,-0.072611,-0.073753,-0.040329,0.012716,0.027419,-0.046656,0.069493,-0.113267,0.058862,0.073865,0.03671,0.035532,-0.045799,-0.009019,-0.054048,0.104597,0.066422,-0.02264,-0.043297,-0.059203,-0.046315,0.059999,-0.053036,-0.05179,-0.026194,-0.013993,-0.047974,0.017777,0.029913,0.026588,0.047681,-0.054755,0.030356,0.026085,0.007739,-0.044213,0.030949,-0.002131,-0.00129,0.007411,-0.0491,0.031506,-0.023145,0.108955,-0.034484,-0.066808,-0.04076,-0.084383,0.034157,0.052127,0.058411,-0.031422,-0.022351,-0.100885,-0.12605,0.038275,-0.041716,-0.035899,0.05793,0.080338,-0.056066,-0.008575,-0.069018,0.156406,-0.040475,-0.008729,-0.060256,-0.03382,-0.000199,-0.048261,-0.020914,0.012721,0.00247,-0.017178,0.044182,-0